{"tid":1631423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(回顧 文長）大家呢幾日都入左迷茫當中 等我同大家回顧下 冷靜下","createTime":"2019-10-06T15:29:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T16:10:58.000Z","uid":152147,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5a3ff8a5449ace9e4ab3a15affd9ac65365a92d3","tid":1631423,"uid":152147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:29:13.000Z","msg":"反送中運動 仲有兩日就正式四個月<br />\n在此之前 香港人一直處於傘運後嘅社運氣氛低迷<br />\n議員被dq 割地兩檢 明日大嶼 <br />\n睇住一個又一個侵害自己利益嘅野通過<br />\n睇住條街越黎越多嘅大陸人<br />\n睇住每日150個新移民落黎<br />\n終於 香港人難得醒左<br />\n由一開始 6.9晚上被清場開始<br />\n香港人學識唔會死佔難佔 識be water<br />\n到6.21 大家竟然夠膽圍警總 <br />\n再到6月尾嘅圍稅局 接收工<br />\nG20團隊眾籌<br />\n到7.1 我地首次反守圍攻 攻入政總 <br />\n就係政總攻佔之後<br />\n我地冇再好似傘運咁留戀金鐘<br />\n反而將示威篇地開花<br />\n好多街坊 中立嘅人係接觸過我地 <br />\n又或者聞過催淚彈之後<br />\n都加入左我地<br />\n慢慢到721中聯辦<br />\n85罷工<br />\n人鍊 榮光<br />\n我地都將呢場革命一次又一次咁推去一個新高度<br />\n加入新嘅元素<br />\n之前有巴打講過<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我地呢刻唔識打 係因為我地未打過順風局</span><br />\n呢句講得無錯 我地今次同以前嘅社運唔同<br />\n我地手上有籌碼 我地有主動權<br />\n變左我地會唔識下一步點做<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">呢個時候 大家望下我上面嘅回顧</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">其實我地一路都經歷過呢啲迷茫</span><br />\n圍唔圍警總 留唔留守 塞鐵 攻唔攻立法會<br />\n到而家嘅私唔私了 陣唔陣地 裝唔裝修 <br />\n點解我地以前可以一齊捱過 而家唔可以<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆 不指責 不督灰</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">連登仔你做唔做到</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">明明我地之前得㗎 點解呢幾日係咁</span><br />\n場革命黎到今日 我地成功將勇武嘅形象打造到入屋<br />\n好多上左年紀嘅師奶 呀伯會覺得佢地型 支持佢地<br />\n但一上連登 大家反而指責佢地 <br />\n唔好忘記 勇武唔係condom<br />\n我知大家未必下下接受佢地嘅行動<br />\n但你可以嘗試了解佢地 嘗試開po表達自己意見<br />\n但唔係開口埋口就屌佢地<br />\n大家呢幾日都好憤怒 但記住梁天琦書中寫到嘅野<br />\n最後 聽日有行動㗎<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">聽日仲要去太子站</span><br />\n大家收拾心情 繼續抗爭啦<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">記住我地好難先去到呢步 唔好呢刻先黎輸盡所有</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你唔認同嘅 嘗試理性發表</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">前線手足全部都有腦思考㗎</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無腦嘅係班黑警</span>"},{"pid":"a1ded09378fbc0759f941f0cbabb2ae95b4f0d50","tid":1631423,"uid":152147,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:30:50.000Z","msg":"打咁多 係真係唔想連登再咁落去<br />\n香港人呢個身分 呢個民族 好應該團結落黎<br />\n共禦外敵"},{"pid":"0c976f9e491ccd66bb50ba035ffd620becdee84a","tid":1631423,"uid":15259,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:31:24.000Z","msg":"對店舖:<br />\n記住<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔需要次次硬裝修</span></span></strong><br />\n可以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">善用</span><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">蟲系魔法</span></strong></span>同埋<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1823</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對人(影大頭相/非主攻類):<br />\n可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong><br />\n唔係下下爆哂缸先叫成功既<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要贏一定要剛柔並用</span>"},{"pid":"6d517d4f55152010f7b59653bac64c57c865db77","tid":1631423,"uid":152147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:31:57.000Z","msg":"希望大家會睇下呢篇野啦 唔啱聽都好 理性討論囉 呢到係討論區<br />\n我地係連登仔 唔係黑警 唔係林鄭 <br />\n理性討論下啦大家"},{"pid":"171f2ee19439114e078e79906ef86724301d1576","tid":1631423,"uid":75959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:32:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">大家 呢幾日都係行動日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但連登都無比大陸DDos攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就證明左係大量五毛做緊野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又分化又風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地係時候要醒下<br />\n<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰<br />\n<br />\n跟住就係開始做正經野：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 推紅色的士撞人單野<br />\n<br />\n2.推黑警又當街踢人單野<br />\n<br />\n3.九龍塘軍營入面有綠色防暴警既片<br />\n<br />\n4.解釋返裝修既原因比外國知<br />\n<br />\n5.宣傳黑紅藍黃既概念<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地唔好再比五毛搞爆連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"f3ce058aa26ec77a299b30f1ee3d923401a951a6","tid":1631423,"uid":152147,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:33:05.000Z","msg":"睇完幫手推 推完我要聽日見到你"},{"pid":"d611f2ff4c8b68c5529b02e101d643528279ded9","tid":1631423,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:33:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"088ce01f21c0f336d6a6852aca5e362b3e8d3128","tid":1631423,"uid":137616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:33:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"89e3c3210a971b2439e1a22d23f3a84bcd1c86c4","tid":1631423,"uid":152147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:33:47.000Z","msg":"如果覺得我五毛嘅自己起我底"},{"pid":"d82c7667565ec4e4f04570e886b7704c4748b966","tid":1631423,"uid":113567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:34:03.000Z","msg":"不割蓆 不指責 不督灰"},{"pid":"a076270c7053ce7381d7abaf1932b22f5f912df2","tid":1631423,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:34:09.000Z","msg":"強烈建議和武合一令星期二香城真正變死城<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631356\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631356</a>"},{"pid":"98edb0f6c6c0344c670c9dd2426b18b4697d6e54","tid":1631423,"uid":125542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:34:17.000Z","msg":"唉 而家係咪都裝修 仲對鋪頭用火魔法<br />\n真心麻麻 我係前線心態都未調整到"},{"pid":"107dab14adb67a2f71e5fa5e41a10aac7de2eb23","tid":1631423,"uid":152147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d611f2ff4c8b68c5529b02e101d643528279ded9","tid":1631423,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:33:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:34:36.000Z","msg":"我都唔太清楚 但印象中聽日話太子站有活動<br />\n冇嘅就18區開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af16b9f10d895b105b63f32e99d356640ad45a89","tid":1631423,"uid":232848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:35:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"130689b8a7ca3935cdb5578dca6358257072410c","tid":1631423,"uid":232848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:35:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f75f089ad5660f07dbc6215ff859e176a31f1baa","tid":1631423,"uid":152147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98edb0f6c6c0344c670c9dd2426b18b4697d6e54","tid":1631423,"uid":125542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:34:17.000Z","msg":"唉 而家係咪都裝修 仲對鋪頭用火魔法<br />\n真心麻麻 我係前線心態都未調整到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:36:24.000Z","msg":"之前有巴打講過 黑裝修 紅裝飾 藍罷買 黃懲罰<br />\n其實好好<br />\n紅裝飾呢part由其出色<br />\n大家諗下一間鋪痴滿連儂牆 係幾靚<br />\n就好似當初大埔連儂隧道一樣"},{"pid":"bb4d09834382e51241b07629d02bad2795a84d94","tid":1631423,"uid":152147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:37:57.000Z","msg":"理性思考會使到我地做出正確嘅決定<br />\n唔好忘記對家等緊我地犯錯 <br />\n大膽假設 小心行事"},{"pid":"9ff600b9290cbb8c331c72b06528a6e26f43972f","tid":1631423,"uid":152147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:38:15.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"dd2648b5693dd211638a583f2d5d8f2b85a91a84","tid":1631423,"uid":152147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:38:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b089439cf28bd21332cfcdf9f471334b345b147","tid":1631423,"uid":152147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:39:03.000Z","msg":"煲底除罩呢個約定大家記得㗎嘛"},{"pid":"22ce592e42c63b6b16d0ad45fb4d3ec175279b00","tid":1631423,"uid":75543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:39:53.000Z","msg":"呢到呢幾日係勁多五毛搞分化 建議手足暫時唔好上連登住 冷靜下先講真 去twitter做文宣好過喺呢到睇post留言<br />\n<br />\n利申: 勇武和理非永不割蓆 齊上齊落"},{"pid":"e4205ee58445891c967d42bfeee7352c20971e94","tid":1631423,"uid":152147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:40:11.000Z","msg":"之前立場篇野都有寫到<br />\n連登就好似有自我復原機制<br />\n屌得再西利都好<br />\n第二日都可以回復正常討論 <br />\n今次大家做唔做到"},{"pid":"d410571b4979d019f7dcf5a4a24fd1af2d81492a","tid":1631423,"uid":152147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22ce592e42c63b6b16d0ad45fb4d3ec175279b00","tid":1631423,"uid":75543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:39:53.000Z","msg":"呢到呢幾日係勁多五毛搞分化 建議手足暫時唔好上連登住 冷靜下先講真 去twitter做文宣好過喺呢到睇post留言<br />\n<br />\n利申: 勇武和理非永不割蓆 齊上齊落"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:41:00.000Z","msg":"每日都好多資訊 好易會飽和 抖下都係好事"},{"pid":"ec41edc9276b69207b6876371e09e1a216a31b30","tid":1631423,"uid":137616,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:41:21.000Z","msg":"一出緊急蒙面 大量人係連登帶風向 <br />\n做到好緊張咁<br />\n其實都係個句 唔捉到就咩事都冇<br />\n捉到都要prove非法集結先 同以前係冇分別<br />\n唔需要升級 一直做落去已經好夠<br />\n佢手到冇哂牌先要推緊急法 明唔明<br />\n<br />\n我地keep住不分化 不割席就夠<br />\n討論做法係要 但都係不完美 可改善<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家要一致對外<br />\n唔理性既討論只係盲屌 冇補於事<br />\n大家冷靜下 知係5毛既請block不推文上一頁<br />\n救連登靠大家<br />\n一齊自我修復"},{"pid":"c5f27bcea14b0b7d38a78dea953ad601319ed69a","tid":1631423,"uid":152147,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:42:01.000Z","msg":"大家睇完之後 一齊努力過好嘛 對家都玩到緊急法<br />\n無棋㗎啦 唔好行錯"}]}